  "title": "AutoAttack",
  "description": "Auto Attack makes it so that holding the attack button autoswings the sword, similar to the combat snapshots",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/yphNcXz/fabric-only-banner.png\" alt=\"Fabric\" width=\"586\" height=\"56\" /></p>\n<h3><strong>Attention Users:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>This is a&nbsp;Fabric mod, it has always been and will always be!</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>You can send suggestions in the comments!</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>I accept pull requests!</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Auto Attack makes it so that holding the attack button autoswings the sword, similar to the combat snapshots.</p>\n<p>Each swing is done right after the attack cooldown is done and thus will always do max possible damage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Features:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Auto Attack</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Auto Bow </strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">(Bow, CrossBow, Trident)</span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Prevents you from hitting blocks</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Attack enemies through obstructions </strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">(similar to CleanCut Mod)</span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Compatible with other mods</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4><strong>Dependencies:</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fabric &gt;= 0.14.9</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Fabric API</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a title=\"Fabric\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"Dependencies\" width=\"149\" height=\"50\" /></strong></a></p>\n<h4><strong>Special Thanks:</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tfarecnim (<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/auto-attack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">inspired by his mod</a>)</li>\n<li>BlazingTwist (<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/anti-tool-break-fabric\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">code inspiration</a>)</li>\n<li>Rongmario (<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cleancut\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">code inspiration</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4><strong>Demonstration:</strong></h4>\n<h2><strong><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/317700834336964608/667813824203718656/2020-01-17_14-34-03.gif\" alt=\"demonstration\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" /></strong></h2>",
